  "instructions": [
    "Chop the romaine lettuce to create the base and distribute half in each serving bowl.",
    "Use a mandoline or box grater to very thinly shave the red cabbage and add to the bowls.",
    "Thinly slice the celery and distribute evenly around the bowls.",
    "Halve the cherry tomatoes and group the halves together on top of each salad.",
    "Slice the avocado and fan the slices on one side of each bowl.",
    "Slice the cucumber into half-moons and arrange on the lettuce.",
    "Peel and grate the carrots and beets separately; add to the salad, keeping beet piles separate.",
    "Place half of the sprouts in the center of each bowl.",
    "Drizzle generously with the dressing and sprinkle with sunflower seeds and pine nuts evenly between the bowls."
